data.description: Gorgeous oversized one-story home in City of Justin proper. Highly sought-after NW-ISD! Owners spared no expense full remodel with flooring, paint, baseboards, crown molding, water heater, and new HVAC systems. 3 bed 2 bath open floorplan with lots of natural light. Spacious study or could be a 4th bedroom area. Porcelain wood-look tile flooring throughout. Large eat-in kitchen with tons of counter space that opens into a huge great room with recently updated woodburning fireplace with stacked stone mantel. The spacious master bedroom includes an ensuite with fully remodeled custom beach entry shower, double vanity, and large walk-in closet with built-ins. Large Secondary bedrooms with walk-in closets & updated 2nd bath. Covered inset patio with fan. Tons of storage everywhere. Community pool, walking trails, playground, and a catch & release fishing pond.
